statements: SELECT * FROM facial_recognition_data;
SELECT id, image_url FROM facial_recognition_data WHERE detected_faces > 5;
SELECT image_url, detected_faces FROM facial_recognition_data WHERE detected_faces = 0;
SELECT * FROM facial_recognition_data WHERE id = 'd3f9765e-7f93-4ac0-8ce3-f4b0d10658ff';
SELECT id, face_identification_result FROM facial_recognition_data WHERE detected_faces IS NULL;
SELECT image_url, detected_faces, face_identification_result FROM facial_recognition_data WHERE detected_faces > 5 ORDER BY detected_faces DESC
SELECT * FROM facial_recognition_data WHERE detected_faces = 0
SELECT id, image_url FROM facial_recognition_data WHERE face_identification_result ->> 'name' = 'John Doe'
SELECT image_url, face_identification_result FROM facial_recognition_data WHERE detected_faces < 3 AND image_url LIKE '%profile%'
SELECT COUNT(id) AS total_faces FROM facial_recognition_data WHERE face_identification_result -> 'confidence' > 0.9
SELECT * FROM facial_recognition_users;
SELECT user_id, full_name, age FROM facial_recognition_users WHERE age >= 18;
SELECT * FROM facial_recognition_users WHERE gender = 'Female';
SELECT username, full_name, TIMESTAMP WITHOUT TIME ZONE '2022-01-01 12:00:00' AS registration_date FROM facial_recognition_users;
SELECT user_id, action FROM facial_recognition_logs WHERE timestamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '1 week';
SELECT * FROM facial_recognition_users WHERE age > 30;
SELECT username, age, gender FROM facial_recognition_users WHERE gender = 'Female';
SELECT full_name, age FROM facial_recognition_users ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT username, action, timestamp FROM facial_recognition_users JOIN facial_recognition_logs ON facial_recognition_users.user_id = facial_recognition_logs.user_id;
SELECT * FROM facial_recognition_logs WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-01' AND action = 'Access Denied';
SELECT * FROM FaceRecognitionUsers;
SELECT user_id, username FROM FaceRecognitionUsers WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT log_id, user_id, timestamp FROM FaceRecognitionLogs ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, image_url FROM FaceRecognitionData WHERE data_type = 'profile';
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS log_count FROM FaceRecognitionLogs GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY log_count DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT user_id, username FROM FaceRecognitionUsers WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426655440000';
SELECT user_id, username, password FROM FaceRecognitionUsers ORDER BY username DESC;
SELECT * FROM FaceRecognitionLogs WHERE action = 'Login' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT data_id, user_id, image_url FROM FaceRecognitionData WHERE data_type = 'profile_picture';

SELECT user_id, recognized_at FROM face_recognition_logs WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000' ORDER BY recognized_at DESC;

SELECT * FROM users WHERE username = 'john_doe';
SELECT user_id, email FROM users ORDER BY email DESC;
SELECT user_id, username, email FROM users WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) FROM user_faces GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
